1
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,980
♪Looking at the bright lights
of the long streets in my hometown♪

2
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:39,480
♪I wrote down
that it's not too late to meet you♪

3
00:00:39,780 --> 00:00:45,260
♪Rereading it now,
I think it's just a joke in life♪

4
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:49,580
♪During my beautiful youth,
I longed for peace♪

5
00:00:49,740 --> 00:00:53,240
♪I vowed to face challenges with you
before Buddha♪

6
00:00:53,940 --> 00:00:59,380
♪I pray to the gods not to be alone♪

7
00:00:59,940 --> 00:01:03,140
♪Singing about farewell at Yang Pass♪

8
00:01:03,340 --> 00:01:06,300
♪Behind the sad song,
no one knows how I feel♪

9
00:01:06,620 --> 00:01:13,100
♪Even though the streets are bustling,
I can only watch alone♪

10
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:16,500
♪Spend years on the sea,
drifting through foreign lands♪

11
00:01:16,780 --> 00:01:20,580
♪There have been
reunions and separations♪

12
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:26,300
♪There are countless sceneries,
none of them are half as good as you♪

13
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,180
♪I asked heaven and earth
where we can share the bright moon♪

14
00:01:30,420 --> 00:01:33,340
♪Looking back,
only the wind understands♪

15
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:39,980
♪Turns out that when love is deep,
right and wrong are forgotten♪

16
00:01:40,260 --> 00:01:43,500
♪Let me ask you
how black hair turns white?♪

17
00:01:43,820 --> 00:01:47,180
♪I answer myself,
saying it's been a long separation♪

18
00:01:47,460 --> 00:01:53,980
♪In the blink of an eye,
I lost my youthful appearance♪

19
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:04,680
=Cao Xuanxuan's Love Journey=

20
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,220
=Episode 14=

21
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:12,670
He Chun.

22
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:14,070
Xuanxuan.

23
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,230
What are you holding?

24
00:02:20,790 --> 00:02:22,230
Before Master Guo's birthday banquet,

25
00:02:22,350 --> 00:02:23,350
Magistrate Guo asked me

26
00:02:23,350 --> 00:02:24,350
to help prepare a gift.

27
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,870
The Western painter's skills
were amazing,

28
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:29,200
so I decided to commission
a painting for Master Guo.

29
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,270
However,

30
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:32,480
his neighbor told me
that the painter had suddenly died.

31
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,190
So I had another painter

32
00:02:34,190 --> 00:02:35,240
make this one instead.

33
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,280
Suddenly died?

34
00:02:41,990 --> 00:02:42,470
He Chun,

35
00:02:42,740 --> 00:02:44,400
can you help me with something?

36
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:47,000
Visit a few places
and gather some information for me.

37
00:02:48,710 --> 00:02:49,150
Got it.

38
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:54,590
Hup!

39
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:01,790
Excuse me.

40
00:03:02,110 --> 00:03:02,830
Can I help you?

41
00:03:02,830 --> 00:03:04,910
Do you know
where the famous Master Zhang

42
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:05,950
is now?

43
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:07,910
Master Zhang?

44
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:10,350
I've lived here my whole life.

45
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:12,200
Never heard of anyone by that name.

46
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,910
Never heard of him?

47
00:03:14,070 --> 00:03:14,670
Never.

48
00:03:20,350 --> 00:03:21,230
Is the Western painter

49
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:22,190
still at your residence?

50
00:03:27,230 --> 00:03:28,430
A few days after you left,

51
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:30,070
we found him

52
00:03:30,070 --> 00:03:30,790
in the cellar.

53
00:03:30,950 --> 00:03:31,790
He'd been tied up

54
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:33,870
and starved to death.

55
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:35,270
Starved to death?

56
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:39,070
Miss He Chun.

57
00:03:39,350 --> 00:03:40,230
What brings you here?

58
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:42,270
I came to ask you something.

59
00:03:42,550 --> 00:03:43,310
Where is Sun Yi?

60
00:03:43,830 --> 00:03:45,110
Sun Yi?

61
00:03:46,230 --> 00:03:47,430
It's odd.

62
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:49,670
After that incident,

63
00:03:49,670 --> 00:03:50,870
I never saw him again.

64
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,710
I heard

65
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:54,550
he left Yan City.

66
00:03:55,470 --> 00:03:56,550
Left Yan City?

67
00:04:01,230 --> 00:04:01,830
Hup!

68
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,110
Xuanxuan.

69
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:05,990
Sit.

70
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:11,430
How's the investigation going?

71
00:04:11,990 --> 00:04:13,150
Sun Yi and Master Zhang

72
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,200
are nowhere to be found.

73
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:15,140
The painter is dead.

74
00:04:19,620 --> 00:04:20,510
As you requested,

75
00:04:20,710 --> 00:04:21,590
I went to Zhao Village

76
00:04:21,590 --> 00:04:22,520
and Lyu Residence.

77
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:23,870
I even questioned people

78
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:24,990
near the Guo Residence.

79
00:04:25,310 --> 00:04:27,030
Sun Yi, Master Zhang, and the painter

80
00:04:27,030 --> 00:04:27,830
are all suspicious.

81
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:30,550
I believe the three of them are tied

82
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:32,590
to whoever is behind

83
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:33,950
all of this.

84
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:39,020
Do we need to tell Magistrate Guo?

85
00:04:40,510 --> 00:04:42,030
I never intended to hide it from him.

86
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:43,470
But he only recently

87
00:04:43,470 --> 00:04:44,510
got back on his feet.

88
00:04:44,910 --> 00:04:46,270
I don't want to overwhelm him.

89
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,740
I'll tell him when the time is right.

90
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:44,580
(Zhai Residence)

91
00:06:09,150 --> 00:06:10,510
(What's going on?)

92
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:12,510
(Is Master leaving again so soon?)

93
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:28,870
Hurry!

94
00:06:35,550 --> 00:06:36,030
Wake up!

95
00:06:36,260 --> 00:06:37,030
How are you feeling?

96
00:06:37,110 --> 00:06:37,830
Wake up!

97
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:38,750
Get up!

98
00:06:38,990 --> 00:06:39,590
Master Zhai.

99
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:41,190
Master Zhai.

100
00:06:44,790 --> 00:06:45,430
Wake up!

101
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:46,710
I...

102
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,910
You wanted to see me?

103
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:06,910
Speak up.

104
00:07:08,350 --> 00:07:09,310
It's nothing.

105
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:10,990
Nothing?

106
00:07:12,350 --> 00:07:13,110
I'm off, then.

107
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:13,940
There's something.

108
00:07:14,790 --> 00:07:15,390
There is...

109
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:16,390
Yes.

110
00:07:16,870 --> 00:07:17,630
There's something.

111
00:07:22,790 --> 00:07:23,310
Right.

112
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:25,230
Chang Zheng confessed

113
00:07:25,670 --> 00:07:26,870
that he mistook the body

114
00:07:26,870 --> 00:07:28,270
for Lian's

115
00:07:28,590 --> 00:07:30,510
because someone left him a note.

116
00:07:31,510 --> 00:07:33,270
Who do you think wrote it?

117
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:36,150
Didn't we discuss this earlier?

118
00:07:36,870 --> 00:07:37,350
Right.

119
00:07:37,550 --> 00:07:38,150
Right...

120
00:07:38,550 --> 00:07:39,710
We did.

121
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:42,710
So, who do you think

122
00:07:42,710 --> 00:07:43,470
wrote it?

123
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,740
Did you hit your head or something?

124
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:52,750
This...

125
00:07:53,110 --> 00:07:53,870
This is for you.

126
00:07:59,910 --> 00:08:00,630
What's this?

127
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,430
Something good.

128
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:07,950
Don't get the wrong idea!

129
00:08:08,710 --> 00:08:09,990
I gave some to Zijie and Xuanxuan

130
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:10,950
too.

131
00:08:15,550 --> 00:08:16,070
Fine.

132
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:17,910
Thanks.

133
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:29,630
Sun Weiyan!

134
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:31,010
Why did you have to run your mouth?

135
00:08:35,100 --> 00:08:38,900
(Tomb of Lian)

136
00:08:49,540 --> 00:08:55,260
(Lian)

137
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:07,340
(Tomb of Lian)

138
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:07,950
Lian.

139
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:11,870
Rest in peace.

140
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,950
I've avenged you.

141
00:09:17,980 --> 00:09:21,300
(Seven days ago, Chang Residence)

142
00:09:54,870 --> 00:09:55,470
Hup!

143
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:27,820
(I know everything you've done.)

144
00:10:27,844 --> 00:10:29,220
(Tomb of Lian)

145
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:30,580
If I had known this would happen,

146
00:10:32,830 --> 00:10:34,870
I wouldn't have listened to your father.

147
00:10:39,470 --> 00:10:41,830
We should've run away together
from the start.

148
00:11:01,660 --> 00:11:03,540
(Yan Administrative Office)

149
00:11:08,070 --> 00:11:08,750
Magistrate Guo!

150
00:11:09,470 --> 00:11:10,150
Magistrate Guo!

151
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:11,390
Wait!

152
00:11:14,870 --> 00:11:15,670
Which one of you

153
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,790
is Magistrate Guo

154
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:19,670
of Yan City?

155
00:11:20,990 --> 00:11:21,510
That's me.

156
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,540
What's the matter?

157
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:25,150
I'm Shangshan, the butler

158
00:11:25,150 --> 00:11:26,150
of the Zhai Residence.

159
00:11:27,230 --> 00:11:27,830
Magistrate Guo,

160
00:11:28,390 --> 00:11:29,270
you must help

161
00:11:29,470 --> 00:11:31,270
my master!

162
00:11:31,280 --> 00:11:32,660
What happened to your master?

163
00:11:35,550 --> 00:11:36,230
Sir.

164
00:11:37,470 --> 00:11:38,950
Do you have a case to report?

165
00:11:41,950 --> 00:11:42,470
Go ahead.

166
00:11:43,310 --> 00:11:43,750
This is

167
00:11:43,750 --> 00:11:44,550
Official Zhou.

168
00:11:44,710 --> 00:11:45,950
He'll be assisting me.

169
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:47,710
I'd prefer to speak

170
00:11:48,070 --> 00:11:49,270
with Magistrate Guo.

171
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:50,910
Sir.

172
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,870
Magistrate Guo is right here.

173
00:11:58,190 --> 00:11:58,950
This way, sir.

174
00:11:59,030 --> 00:11:59,830
My master...

175
00:11:59,830 --> 00:12:00,750
We'll talk inside.

176
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:02,270
Don't worry.

177
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,420
Whatever the matter,

178
00:12:03,460 --> 00:12:05,230
I will get to the bottom of it.

179
00:12:05,740 --> 00:12:07,390
This incident happened three days ago.

180
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,110
Why didn't you report it sooner?

181
00:12:09,990 --> 00:12:11,510
Up until a few days ago,

182
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:13,920
Master Zhai was preoccupied
with spiritual cultivation

183
00:12:14,830 --> 00:12:16,070
and rarely returned.

184
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:17,830
He instructed us

185
00:12:18,750 --> 00:12:20,550
not to disturb him,

186
00:12:20,830 --> 00:12:21,710
even if

187
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:24,230
he didn't come home for days.

188
00:12:24,830 --> 00:12:25,710
He even told us

189
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:28,510
not to be startled

190
00:12:28,830 --> 00:12:30,390
if anything frightening happened.

191
00:12:31,790 --> 00:12:33,030
We thought

192
00:12:33,190 --> 00:12:34,470
it was perhaps

193
00:12:34,710 --> 00:12:37,550
part of some spiritual practice.

194
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:38,790
Besides,

195
00:12:39,590 --> 00:12:41,270
even if something terrible

196
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:42,470
had happened to him,

197
00:12:43,230 --> 00:12:44,830
there would be a body.

198
00:12:45,070 --> 00:12:45,870
He wouldn't have

199
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,190
completely vanished

200
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:49,790
into thin air!

201
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,750
Then why are you

202
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:53,790
reporting this now?

203
00:12:54,430 --> 00:12:55,310
A few days ago,

204
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:56,750
I heard rumors

205
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,230
about dismembered remains being found.

206
00:13:00,910 --> 00:13:01,990
I didn't pay much attention

207
00:13:02,230 --> 00:13:03,430
at the time.

208
00:13:04,350 --> 00:13:05,790
But last night,

209
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:06,750
I heard

210
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:07,710
that the remains

211
00:13:07,710 --> 00:13:08,790
were male.

212
00:13:09,190 --> 00:13:10,230
How could I

213
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:12,830
possibly stay calm?

214
00:13:13,510 --> 00:13:14,470
Master Zhai

215
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:15,800
has always been kind to me.

216
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:16,910
After so many years...

217
00:13:20,110 --> 00:13:22,230
Oh, Master Zhai...

218
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:23,630
Bring him a chair.

219
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:34,710
Calm down, sir.

220
00:13:34,990 --> 00:13:35,670
Take your time.

221
00:13:35,960 --> 00:13:37,880
Does Master Zhai have
any distinctive marks

222
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:39,670
on his legs for identification?

223
00:13:41,470 --> 00:13:42,310
I...

224
00:13:42,830 --> 00:13:44,150
I'm not sure about his legs.

225
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,190
I do recall

226
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,630
he had

227
00:13:48,230 --> 00:13:49,710
a scar

228
00:13:49,710 --> 00:13:50,950
on his left arm.

229
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:53,110
The first arm we found

230
00:13:53,310 --> 00:13:54,070
was the right arm.

231
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,910
We can't yet confirm

232
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:58,510
if the arm and the leg
belong to the same person.

233
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:00,590
We thought

234
00:14:00,590 --> 00:14:01,790
the remains belonged to Lian.

235
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:04,350
In any case,

236
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,190
Master Zhai has gone missing,

237
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:08,830
and it's highly likely
he met with foul play.

238
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:11,630
What about the sedan bearers?

239
00:14:12,470 --> 00:14:13,710
We brought

240
00:14:14,190 --> 00:14:15,710
them back.

241
00:14:16,030 --> 00:14:17,070
The physician said

242
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:19,190
they had been drugged with a heavy dose.

243
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,080
We gave them several doses of medicine.

244
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:22,790
Fearing another incident,

245
00:14:23,230 --> 00:14:24,230
I had the servants

246
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:25,710
watch over them.

247
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:26,990
They didn't wake up

248
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:29,830
until the evening of the following day.

249
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:32,110
I questioned them repeatedly.

250
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:33,910
They said

251
00:14:34,790 --> 00:14:36,270
they were knocked unconscious

252
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:38,220
shortly after leaving the residence.

253
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:43,550
Based on the timing and distance,

254
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:45,470
it's unlikely the bearers were involved.

255
00:14:46,710 --> 00:14:47,390
Sir,

256
00:14:47,950 --> 00:14:48,830
can you tell us

257
00:14:49,110 --> 00:14:50,950
how many people are in the Zhai family?

258
00:14:51,430 --> 00:14:52,350
13

259
00:14:52,550 --> 00:14:53,910
in total.

260
00:14:55,990 --> 00:14:56,510
What?

261
00:14:57,660 --> 00:14:59,880
Do you suspect it's someone
within the household?

262
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:02,190
It's just a theory.

263
00:15:02,750 --> 00:15:04,830
If the dismembered body
belongs to Master Zhai,

264
00:15:05,430 --> 00:15:06,430
then the murderer

265
00:15:06,830 --> 00:15:08,350
must harbor a deep grudge against him.

266
00:15:09,310 --> 00:15:09,730
True.

267
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:11,710
Investigate

268
00:15:12,110 --> 00:15:13,870
Master Zhai's relationships thoroughly.

269
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:14,670
Understood.

270
00:15:15,830 --> 00:15:16,550
He Chun.

271
00:15:16,550 --> 00:15:17,270
Go with him.

272
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:53,790
Well?

273
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:57,430
Based on the deceased's
skeletal structure,

274
00:15:57,790 --> 00:15:58,950
the victim was male,

275
00:15:59,590 --> 00:16:00,310
approximately

276
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:01,670
60 years old,

277
00:16:02,310 --> 00:16:03,630
and about 170 cm tall.

278
00:16:04,350 --> 00:16:05,830
The thigh was cleanly severed,

279
00:16:06,350 --> 00:16:08,350
likely with a very sharp blade.

280
00:16:09,030 --> 00:16:10,910
Judging by the degree of decomposition,

281
00:16:11,190 --> 00:16:12,710
the victim died about three days ago.

282
00:16:13,350 --> 00:16:15,150
In the past year,

283
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:18,150
only Master Zhai's physical description
matches the victim.

284
00:16:19,230 --> 00:16:20,430
This is likely Master Zhai.

285
00:16:22,110 --> 00:16:24,030
Who could be so cruel?

286
00:16:24,590 --> 00:16:26,670
Killing a man
and then dismembering his body?

287
00:16:29,470 --> 00:16:30,150
Why is he here?

288
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:34,630
If that's the case,

289
00:16:35,640 --> 00:16:36,470
it's highly probable

290
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:38,320
that someone in the Zhai family
committed it.

291
00:16:38,350 --> 00:16:39,150
That's impossible.

292
00:16:39,830 --> 00:16:41,230
According to Shangshan,

293
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,750
Master Zhai was alive

