00:32:09,670 --> 00:32:10,790
Who knows

592
00:32:10,790 --> 00:32:11,950
when we'll find water again?

593
00:32:12,470 --> 00:32:13,030
Hand it over.

594
00:32:35,510 --> 00:32:37,070
The flower looks lovely on you.

595
00:32:44,510 --> 00:32:45,590
Just the flower?

596
00:32:50,110 --> 00:32:50,790
What's wrong?

597
00:33:02,670 --> 00:33:04,670
Finally, two easy targets.

598
00:33:07,710 --> 00:33:08,270
Search them.

599
00:33:12,310 --> 00:33:13,230
Please, have mercy!

600
00:33:13,230 --> 00:33:14,070
Mercy, my lady!

601
00:33:14,590 --> 00:33:16,310
Instead of earning an honest living,

602
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:17,790
you're doing these harmful deeds.

603
00:33:18,190 --> 00:33:19,070
Please, have mercy.

604
00:33:19,190 --> 00:33:20,390
Give us another chance.

605
00:33:20,390 --> 00:33:21,710
We won't dare do this again.

606
00:33:21,710 --> 00:33:22,750
We're only doing this

607
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:23,670
out of desperation.

608
00:33:23,670 --> 00:33:24,700
We won't do it again.

609
00:33:24,700 --> 00:33:25,590
We're serious!

610
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:27,030
Please give us another chance.

611
00:33:27,350 --> 00:33:28,310
If there's a next time,

612
00:33:28,750 --> 00:33:29,630
I won't let you off.

613
00:33:29,910 --> 00:33:30,350
Now go!

614
00:33:30,590 --> 00:33:31,390
Yes...

615
00:33:31,390 --> 00:33:31,950
Hurry!

616
00:33:31,950 --> 00:33:33,750
Thank you!

617
00:33:33,750 --> 00:33:34,470
Come on!

618
00:33:44,870 --> 00:33:45,510
Sun Weiyan?

619
00:33:45,910 --> 00:33:46,670
Sun Weiyan?

620
00:33:47,870 --> 00:33:48,550
Come on.

621
00:33:49,150 --> 00:33:50,390
Let's get out of here.

622
00:34:04,390 --> 00:34:05,150
Sun Weiyan!

623
00:34:07,030 --> 00:34:07,590
I'm fine.

624
00:34:08,030 --> 00:34:09,190
It's minor.

625
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,940
You don't even know martial arts.

626
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:11,980
Why shield me?

627
00:34:11,990 --> 00:34:13,310
I'm a man.

628
00:34:13,310 --> 00:34:14,790
I couldn't put you in danger.

629
00:34:15,630 --> 00:34:16,910
You fool.

630
00:34:17,950 --> 00:34:18,990
I'll go deal with them.

631
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:19,710
No need.

632
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,800
We'll get someone
to take care of them later.

633
00:34:22,070 --> 00:34:22,630
Let's go.

634
00:34:30,980 --> 00:34:34,420
(Yan Administrative Office)

635
00:34:36,590 --> 00:34:37,350
Zijie...

636
00:34:38,190 --> 00:34:39,030
What happened to you?

637
00:34:40,230 --> 00:34:40,910
Don't ask.

638
00:34:40,910 --> 00:34:41,830
Ran into a crooked inn.

639
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:42,870
Are you all right?

640
00:34:43,350 --> 00:34:43,910
I'm fine.

641
00:34:44,030 --> 00:34:45,510
He Chun already helped bandage me up.

642
00:34:45,870 --> 00:34:47,150
I let myself go for just a while,

643
00:34:47,150 --> 00:34:48,580
and Yan City has become such a mess.

644
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:49,750
Oh, right.

645
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:50,830
This is the master diviner

646
00:34:50,830 --> 00:34:52,350
I told you about.

647
00:34:57,470 --> 00:34:58,150
Sir,

648
00:34:58,870 --> 00:34:59,910
I'd be most grateful

649
00:35:00,040 --> 00:35:00,950
for your assistance.

650
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:03,550
Spare me the small talk.

651
00:35:03,990 --> 00:35:04,910
Give me liquor

652
00:35:05,990 --> 00:35:06,590
or

653
00:35:07,230 --> 00:35:07,870
give me money.

654
00:35:11,110 --> 00:35:11,870
Pay him, then.

655
00:35:21,310 --> 00:35:22,910
I've heard the story.

656
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:24,390
Take me to the scene.

657
00:35:24,950 --> 00:35:25,470
All right.

658
00:35:56,360 --> 00:36:02,240
♪Like the setting sun,
which repeatedly sets in the west♪

659
00:36:03,500 --> 00:36:08,940
♪My heart goes over mountains
to rest with you♪

660
00:36:10,100 --> 00:36:13,540
♪As the winds and clouds shift,
our encounter♪

661
00:36:13,540 --> 00:36:17,300
♪Seems like the perfect foreshadowing♪

662
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:22,740
♪But it was a misplaced expectation♪

663
00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:27,340
♪I think I'm exceptionally affectionate♪

664
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:30,460
♪Devotion can warm the coldest ice♪

665
00:36:30,820 --> 00:36:34,020
♪And you're a shooting star
that flashes by♪

666
00:36:34,460 --> 00:36:36,740
♪Out of reach♪

667
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:41,020
♪I prayed for a miracle countless times♪

668
00:36:41,300 --> 00:36:45,420
♪If I meet you, I only wish
we could be together forever♪

669
00:36:45,700 --> 00:36:51,820
♪But only the distant phantom remains♪

670
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:54,980
♪Love rises like the wind
but remains unsettled when it stops♪

671
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:58,260
♪Chasing you through four seasons,
wandering for a lifetime♪

672
00:36:58,540 --> 00:37:00,220
♪Fish in the water♪

673
00:37:00,220 --> 00:37:05,460
♪Is greedy for the reflection
of clouds in the heart of the lake♪

674
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:08,580
♪From dusk to dawn,
from heavy snow to early clear sky♪

675
00:37:08,780 --> 00:37:13,100
♪Searching for your footprints
from south to west♪

676
00:37:13,460 --> 00:37:19,100
♪The wind stops,
but the dream isn't over♪
